  <entry>
    <title>FastAPI + psutil + Chart.js：轻量系统监控仪表盘容器化</title>
    <url>/2026/07/19/fastapi-system-monitor-dashboard/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>这是一个基于 FastAPI、psutil 和 Chart.js 的轻量系统监控项目。后端负责采集 CPU、内存、磁盘、网络和进程数据，前端定时请求 REST API，再将数据绘制成动态图表。</p>
<h2 id="项目结构"><a href="#项目结构" class="headerlink" title="项目结构"></a>项目结构</h2><figure class="highlight text"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">monitor/</span><br><span class="line">├── app/</span><br><span class="line">│   ├── app.py</span><br><span class="line">│   ├── collector.py</span><br><span class="line">│   └── api/routes.py</span><br><span class="line">├── static/index.html</span><br><span class="line">├── requirements.txt</span><br><span class="line">├── Dockerfile</span><br><span class="line">└── docker-compose.yml</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>依赖非常精简：</p>
<figure class="highlight text"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">fastapi</span><br><span class="line">uvicorn</span><br><span class="line">psutil</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>FastAPI 同时提供 API 和静态页面，因此不需要再单独启动一个前端开发服务器。</p>
<h2 id="API-设计"><a href="#API-设计" class="headerlink" title="API 设计"></a>API 设计</h2><table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th>路径</th>
<th>数据</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody><tr>
<td><code>/api/cpu</code></td>
<td>逻辑核心数、物理核心数、CPU 使用率</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><code>/api/memory</code></td>
<td>总内存、已用内存、可用内存、使用率</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><code>/api/disks</code></td>
<td>分区、挂载点、文件系统与使用率</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><code>/api/network</code></td>
<td>累计流量与上传、下载速度</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><code>/api/processes</code></td>
<td>按 CPU 排序的进程列表</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
<p>主应用挂载静态目录并返回首页：</p>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">app = FastAPI()</span><br><span class="line">app.mount(<span class="string">&quot;/static&quot;</span>, StaticFiles(directory=<span class="string">&quot;static&quot;</span>), name=<span class="string">&quot;static&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">@app.get(<span class="params"><span class="string">&quot;/&quot;</span></span>)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">index</span>():</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> FileResponse(<span class="string">&quot;static/index.html&quot;</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>这种结构适合小型仪表盘：部署单一、跨域问题少，也容易打包进一个容器。</p>
<h2 id="用-psutil-采集系统指标"><a href="#用-psutil-采集系统指标" class="headerlink" title="用 psutil 采集系统指标"></a>用 psutil 采集系统指标</h2><p>CPU 和内存数据可以直接读取：</p>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">get_cpu</span>():</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="string">&quot;逻辑核心数&quot;</span>: psutil.cpu_count(logical=<span class="literal">True</span>),</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="string">&quot;物理核心数&quot;</span>: psutil.cpu_count(logical=<span class="literal">False</span>),</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="string">&quot;CPU使用率&quot;</span>: psutil.cpu_percent(interval=<span class="number">0.2</span>),</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>网络速度则需要做两次采样：</p>
<figure class="highlight text"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">第一次读取累计字节数</span><br><span class="line">        ↓ 等待固定时间</span><br><span class="line">第二次读取累计字节数</span><br><span class="line">        ↓</span><br><span class="line">两次差值 ÷ 采样时间 = 传输速度</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>进程 CPU 使用率同样需要预热采样，否则第一次调用通常得到 0。项目先遍历进程触发采样，短暂等待后再读取并排序。</p>
<h2 id="前端可视化"><a href="#前端可视化" class="headerlink" title="前端可视化"></a>前端可视化</h2><p>前端使用 Chart.js 展示：</p>
<ul>
<li>CPU 使用率折线图；</li>
<li>内存占用饼图；</li>
<li>网络上传与下载曲线；</li>
<li>可搜索、可排序的进程表格；</li>
<li>深色模式和响应式卡片布局。</li>
</ul>
<p>前端轮询简单直观，但请求过密会增加采样开销。进一步优化时，可以让后端在后台统一采样，再通过 WebSocket 或 Server-Sent Events 推送给多个客户端。</p>
<h2 id="Docker-化"><a href="#Docker-化" class="headerlink" title="Docker 化"></a>Docker 化</h2><p>镜像基于 <code>python:3.12-slim</code>：</p>
<figure class="highlight dockerfile"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">FROM</span> python:<span class="number">3.12</span>-slim</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">WORKDIR</span><span class="language-bash"> /app</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">COPY</span><span class="language-bash"> app/ ./app/</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">COPY</span><span class="language-bash"> static/ ./static/</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">COPY</span><span class="language-bash"> requirements.txt ./</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">RUN</span><span class="language-bash"> pip install --no-cache-dir -r requirements.txt</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">EXPOSE</span> <span class="number">1000</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">CMD</span><span class="language-bash"> [<span class="string">&quot;uvicorn&quot;</span>, <span class="string">&quot;app.app:app&quot;</span>, <span class="string">&quot;--host&quot;</span>, <span class="string">&quot;0.0.0.0&quot;</span>, <span class="string">&quot;--port&quot;</span>, <span class="string">&quot;1000&quot;</span>]</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>Compose 只需要构建镜像并映射端口：</p>
<figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">services:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">monitor:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">build:</span> <span class="string">.</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">container_name:</span> <span class="string">system_monitor</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">ports:</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="string">&quot;1000:1000&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">restart:</span> <span class="string">always</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>启动命令：</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">docker compose up -d --build</span><br><span class="line">docker compose ps</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>访问：</p>
<figure class="highlight text"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">http://127.0.0.1:1000/</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="容器监控的边界"><a href="#容器监控的边界" class="headerlink" title="容器监控的边界"></a>容器监控的边界</h2><p>默认情况下，容器中的 psutil 主要看到容器自己的进程和命名空间，它不天然等于“完整宿主机监控”。如果希望读取宿主机的全部进程、磁盘和网络信息，需要额外挂载 <code>/proc</code>、使用宿主机 PID 命名空间，或把采集器直接运行在宿主机。</p>
<p>这些方式会提高权限和攻击面，因此不能只为了数据更完整就盲目使用 <code>privileged: true</code>。更稳妥的选择是：</p>
<ol>
<li>明确需要哪些指标；</li>
<li>只挂载必要的只读目录；</li>
<li>为监控页面增加认证；</li>
<li>不把进程列表直接暴露到公网；</li>
<li>为采集接口增加超时、缓存和访问频率限制。</li>
</ol>
<h2 id="后续改进"><a href="#后续改进" class="headerlink" title="后续改进"></a>后续改进</h2><ul>
<li>加入磁盘 IO、温度和 GPU 指标；</li>
<li>使用 WebSocket 推送；</li>
<li>为历史数据接入 SQLite、Prometheus 或时序数据库；</li>
<li>增加登录认证和反向代理；</li>
<li>区分容器指标与宿主机指标；</li>
<li>为异常阈值增加告警。</li>
</ul>
<p>这个项目让我把 Python 数据采集、REST API、前端可视化和容器部署串成了一条完整链路，也更清楚地理解了容器隔离对监控数据的影响。</p>
]]></content>
      <categories>
        <category>开发</category>
        <category>云原生</category>
        <category>Python</category>
        <category>Docker</category>
      </categories>
      <tags>
        <tag>Python</tag>
        <tag>Docker</tag>
        <tag>FastAPI</tag>
        <tag>psutil</tag>
        <tag>Chart.js</tag>
      </tags>
  </entry>
